W. L. PAYNE, Debtor, v. The UNION MORTGAGE AND INVESTMENT COMPANY. No. 1804. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. Dec. 13, 1938. Williamson, Cubbison & Vaughan, of Kansas City, Kan., for appellant. McAnany, Alden & Van Cleave, of Kansas City, Kan., for appellee.

Before LEWIS and PHILLIPS, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed at appellant’s costs, pursuant to stipulation.
